# Always Deploy Latest

When any codebase in `hybridcloud/` changes:

## Operator Charts
1. Bump `helm/Chart.yaml` version
2. Run `make upload-*-chart` in bootstrap or operator directory
3. Update `bootstrap/helm/central/values.yaml`

## Dashboard / UI Images
1. Bump image tags in make targets
2. Run build-push targets
3. Update central values.yaml

## EDA Decision Environments
1. Rebuild affected DE images
2. Push to Quay
3. Recreate activations via `infra.aap_configuration`
